# 🌐 Real-Time Chat Backend

A globally hosted real-time chat backend built with **Node.js**, **Express**, and **Socket.IO**.  
Supports private messaging, group chats, and automatic cleanup of user sessions. All data is stored **in memory**, with **no database**.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Global chat access — anyone using the frontend can join
- Real-time private and group messaging
- User presence and typing indicators
- No database — memory-only data handling
- Auto-removal of disconnected users
- Group chat messages visible only to members

---

## 🛠️ Technologies

- Node.js
- Express
- Socket.IO
- UUID

---

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/realtime-chat-backend.git
cd realtime-chat-backend
npm install
